H0.text: A single cell becomes many cells is the best description of the development of a human embryo.

H1.text: Each cell has a different function is the statement that best describes the development of a human embryo.

H2.text: Many cells combine to form one cell best describes the development of a human embryo.

H3.text: All the cells have the same function is the statement that best describes the development of a human embryo.

A4.text: growth from a one-celled zygote to an adult human being.
